854
00:49:19,153 --> 00:49:22,088
Oh, where's John?
He said he'd walk with me.

855
00:49:22,156 --> 00:49:24,420
John is no longer
staying here.

856
00:49:24,491 --> 00:49:25,856
Shot through
this morning,

857
00:49:25,926 --> 00:49:27,518
