01:26:05,123 --> 01:26:06,317
You haven't got a chance
this way.

1538
01:26:06,391 --> 01:26:07,380
What do you want?

1539
01:26:07,459 --> 01:26:08,756
You might as well give up.

1540
01:26:08,827 --> 01:26:10,556
