"lt" is appalling.

1541
01:26:10,629 --> 01:26:12,563
He is dreadful.

1542
01:26:12,631 --> 01:26:14,360
Come back!

1543
01:26:14,432 --> 01:26:16,764
I have never in my life
seen anything

1544
01:26:16,835 --> 01:26:19,065
in the same category
of hideousness,

1545
01:26:19,137 --> 01:26:20,570
but I adore him!

