[Laughs]

1555
01:27:08,253 --> 01:27:09,914
Ah.

1556
01:27:09,988 --> 01:27:11,649
[Screaming]

1557
01:27:15,794 --> 01:27:18,262
Hurry!

1558
01:27:18,330 --> 01:27:19,661
Hurry!

1559
01:27:19,731 --> 01:27:21,995
Gina!

1560
01:27:22,067 --> 01:27:24,126
[Both screaming]

1561
