1630
01:33:33,905 --> 01:33:35,964
[Clock ticking]

1631
01:33:43,047 --> 01:33:45,140
Pauline; I am writing
a little of this up

1632
01:33:45,216 --> 01:33:48,481
on the morning
before the death.

1633
01:33:48,553 --> 01:33:51,021
I felt very excited and...

1634
01:33:51,089 --> 01:33:54,388
The-Night-Before-Christmas-ish
