Let's go upstairs,
Deborah.

1668
01:36:09,494 --> 01:36:12,622
I wrote the first 10 pages
of my opera last night.

1669
01:36:12,697 --> 01:36:14,187
All right, then.

1670
01:36:17,001 --> 01:36:18,832
[Sighs]

1671
